City of St. Louis Boundary

Source: R/stl_sf_boundary.R
stl_sf_boundary.Rd

A simple features data set containing a single polygon with the extent of the City of St. Louis's boundary.

data(stl_sf_boundary)

Format

A simple feature with 1 rows and 5 variables:

GEOID

county FIPS code

NAME

polygon name

LAND_SQMI

land area of city, square miles

WATER_SQMI

water area of city, square miles

geometry

simple features geometry
